Well, you decide.
I thought the game is as easy to control with a gamepad as Creepy Tale, or Creaks, but turned out it's a Point & Click game.

- Flaws:
• confusing game, which is impossible to play without youtube walkthroughs when you play for the first time;
• you have to save the game often, because the game or pc can get stuck and you can lose all the progress;
• ugly menu;
• annoying mini-games, and especially it's another game with musical puzzle [wtf?!];
• the price is pretty high for such the game.

+ Benefits:
• playing flawlessly the game takes 1.5 h.
